---
const faqs = [
  {
    question: "How quickly will I see results?",
    answer: "Most men start seeing positive changes within the first week of applying the strategies. However, every situation is different. Some guys escape the friend zone within days, while others take a few weeks to see major breakthroughs. The average time to significant results is 18 days based on our community feedback."
  },
  {
    question: "Will this work if I'm already deep in the friend zone?",
    answer: "Yes! In fact, some of our biggest success stories come from men who were \"best friends\" for months or even years. The deeper you are, the more powerful the transformation when you apply the Friend Zone Escape Protocol correctly. Chapter 4 specifically addresses long-term friend zone situations."
  },
  {
    question: "Is this manipulative or dishonest?",
    answer: "Absolutely not. Everything we teach is about becoming genuinely more attractive and confident. We focus on authentic self-improvement, better communication, and understanding psychology - not tricks or manipulation. You'll still be you, just the best version of yourself."
  },
  {
    question: "What if I'm shy or introverted?",
    answer: "Perfect! Many of our most successful students are introverts. The blueprint includes specific strategies for shy guys, including how to use your natural qualities as strengths. You don't need to become an extrovert - you just need to communicate your value effectively."
  },
  {
    question: "Do I need to be physically attractive or wealthy?",
    answer: "Not at all. While these things can help, they're not necessary for attraction. The blueprint focuses on the psychological triggers that create attraction, which are much more powerful than looks or money. We have success stories from men of all ages, backgrounds, and physical appearances."
  },
  {
    question: "What format is the blueprint in?",
    answer: "You'll receive a comprehensive 147-page PDF guide that you can read on any device. It's organized into clear chapters with actionable steps, real examples, and practical exercises. Plus, you get all the bonus materials in easily downloadable formats."
  },
  {
    question: "Is there ongoing support?",
    answer: "Yes! You get lifetime access to our private community where you can ask questions, share progress, and get support from other men on the same journey. We also have weekly live Q&A calls and expert coaching available."
  },
  {
    question: "What if it doesn't work for me?",
    answer: "We offer a 60-day money-back guarantee. If you apply the strategies and don't see improvement in your dating life, simply email us for a full refund. We stand behind our product because we've seen it work for thousands of men."
  },
  {
    question: "Can I use this for online dating too?",
    answer: "Absolutely! While the core blueprint focuses on in-person interactions, many principles apply to online dating. Plus, the bonus \"Text Message Templates\" are specifically designed for digital communication and dating apps."
  },
  {
    question: "How is this different from other dating advice?",
    answer: "Most dating advice is generic and theoretical. The Unfriendzoned Blueprint is a specific, step-by-step system based on psychology and tested with over 10,000 men. It focuses specifically on the friend zone problem, not general dating advice."
  }
];
---

<section id="faq" class="section-padding bg-white dark:bg-slate-900">
  <div class="container-custom">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold mb-6">
        Frequently Asked <span class="text-gradient">Questions</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Get answers to the most common questions about the Unfriendzoned Blueprint
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <!-- FAQ Items -->
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      {faqs.map((faq, _index) => (
        <div class="mb-6 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
          <details class="group">
            <summary class="flex justify-between items-center p-6 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-slate-700 transition-colors">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white pr-4">
                {faq.question}
              </h3>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180 flex-shrink-0" 
                   fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
              </svg>
            </summary>
            <div class="px-6 pb-6">
              <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                {faq.answer}
              </p>
            </div>
          </details>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
    
    <!-- Still Have Questions -->
    <div class="text-center mt-16">
      <div class="bg-primary-50 dark:bg-primary-900/20 rounded-2xl p-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
          Still Have Questions?
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">
          Our support team is here to help. Get answers within 24 hours.
        </p>
        <a 
          href="mailto:support@unfriendzoned.com" 
          class="btn-secondary inline-block"
        >
          Contact Support
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  details[open] summary {
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }
  
  .dark details[open] summary {
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }
</style> 